        <pb n="5"/>
        <head rend="align(centre)">THE BOY'S<lb/>PICTURE BOOK.</head><lb/>
        <p rend="align(centre)">&rule;</p>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>47K42</name>
                <desc>fishing net</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">This is a net to catch fish.<lb/>They catch a great many at<lb/>one time with the
            net.</p>
        <p>&drule;</p>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>43C121(+41614)</name>
                <desc>angling (+ fish-hook)</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">Here is a fish hook.<lb/>Only one fish is caught at a<lb/>time with the hook</p>
        
        <pb n="6"/>
        <fw type="pagenumber" rend="align(centre)">4</fw>
        <fw rend="align(centre)">&drule;</fw><lb/>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>46C1451</name>
                <desc>covered wagon, hooded wagon</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">This is a picture of a<lb/>Wagon, formerly used to<lb/>travel to Ohio. They go
            very<lb/>slow&mdash;only three miles in an<lb/>hour.</p>
        <p>&drule;</p>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>46C26</name>
                <desc>steamsailer</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">Here is a Steamboat,<lb/>which goes much faster than<lb/>a wagon. It will go twelve<lb/>miles an hour. It has
            very<lb/>handsome rooms in it.</p>
        
        <pb n="7"/>
        <fw type="pagenumber" rend="align(centre)">5</fw>
        <fw rend="align(centre)">&drule;</fw><lb/>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>46C1521</name>
                <desc>steam locomotive</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">Here is a Railroad<lb/>Car, filled with people go&ndash;<lb type="inWord"/>ing twenty or thirty miles
            in<lb/>an hour. Some of these cars<lb/>will hold fifty people. You<lb/>can go as far
            in one day in<lb/>this car, as you can in twelve<lb/>or fifteen days in the
            wagon.<lb/>The locomotive is forward<lb/>of the passenger car. See<lb/>the smoke
            issue out of it!<lb/>It looks very beautiful in the<lb/>night to see the
            locomotive.</p>
        
        <pb n="8"/>
        <fw type="pagenumber" rend="align(centre)">6</fw>
        <fw rend="align(centre)">&drule;</fw><lb/>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>25G4</name>
                <desc>(WHEAT)	plants and herbs: wheat</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">This is a sheaf of wheat<lb/>ready to be carried to the<lb/>barn, and thrashed.
            Flour<lb/>is made of wheat, and cakes<lb/>are made of flour. Children<lb/>love to eat
            good warm cakes.</p>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">Did you ever see wheat<lb/>growing in the fields? It<lb/>then looks very beautiful.
            It<lb/>sometimes grows 5 feet high.</p>
        
        <pb n="9"/>
        <fw type="pagenumber" rend="align(centre)">7</fw>
        <fw rend="align(centre)">&drule;</fw><lb/>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>43C722</name>
                <desc>(playing with) top</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">Here is a picture of a top.<lb/>A top will spin round. Ed&ndash;<lb type="inWord"/>ward, please make my
            top<lb/>spin round.</p>
        <p>&drule;</p>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>46C232</name>
                <desc>rowing-boat, canoe, etc.</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">See the boy in the boat.<lb/>He makes the boat go with<lb/>an oar or paddle, which
            he<lb/>holds in his hands.</p>
        
        <pb n="10"/>
        <fw type="pagenumber" rend="align(centre)">8</fw>
        <fw rend="align(centre)">&drule;</fw><lb/>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>49M11</name>
                <desc>printing press</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">Here is a printing<lb/>press. By this, books and<lb/>newspapers are printed.</p>
        <p>&drule;</p>
        <figure rend="align(centre)">
            <ic:iconClass>
                <name>46C121</name>
                <desc>carrying something</desc>
            </ic:iconClass>
        </figure>
        <p rend="first-indent(2)">See this boy carrying a<lb/>pocket book. It is a great<lb/>load for such a small
            boy.</p>
